data.description: Welcome HOME to this elegant 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home in Reynoldsburg's Leighton Village, featuring bamboo flooring in the dining and kitchen areas, vaulted ceilings, and an open-concept layout ideal for entertaining. Enjoy the convenience of a first-floor laundry and an extra room above the garage perfect for an office or craft room. Outside, relax on a spacious deck or entertain on the stamped concrete patio, complemented by a large Amish-made shed for additional storage. Perfectly located in a welcoming community, this home offers both luxury and practicality.  Shed (2023), concrete patio (2023), basement waterproofing (2023). gutter leaf guards (2022).
